data.description: Welcome to Tumwater! This home is all about the LOCATION!!!  Great for a first-time home buyer or investor!  Conveniently located to local shopping, restaurants, the freeway, way too many amenities  to list them all! Home is in need of a little TLC, but could still possibly go FHA or VA.    Home may be used for commercial use, buyer to verify all information to their satisfaction.   Listing agent Bea Barnes will   be providing a 1 (yr) American Home Shield Plus Warranty to buyer at closing.  $10,000 seller credit to go toward buyer buy down rate or closing cost another  $5,000 seller credit to go toward new flooring, total of $15,0000 seller concessions.  Don't wait! This home won't be on the market much longer!
